#: .\dashboard\views.py:436
msgid "Transporte Público"
msgstr "Public Transport"

#: .\dashboard\views.py:438
msgid ""
"¡Bien hecho! Ha plantado 13 árboles, con esto has logrado contrarrestar el "
"CO2 al usar trasporte publico. obtuviste tu primera insignia. ¡Sigue así y "
"ayuda a hacer del mundo un lugar más verde y saludable!"
msgstr ""
"Well done! You've planted 13 trees, and by doing so, you've managed to counteract the"
"CO2 from using public transportation. You've earned your first badge. Keep it up and"
"help make the world a greener and healthier place!"

#: .\dashboard\views.py:441
msgid "Automovil"
msgstr "Car"

#: .\dashboard\views.py:443
msgid ""
"¡Felicidades! con la siembra de 76 arboles lograste capturar el CO2 que "
"genera un carro. Sigue así y pronto tendrás tu segunda insignia."
msgstr ""
"Congratulations! with the planting of 76 trees you managed to capture the CO2 "
"generated by one car. Keep it up and soon you will have your second badge."

#: .\dashboard\views.py:445
msgid "Moto"
msgstr "Motorcycle"

#: .\dashboard\views.py:447
msgid ""
"¡Muy bien! Has plantado 10 árboles mas y lograste capturar el equivalente de "
"emisión de CO2 de una Moto, Continúa cuidando de ellos, pronto obtendrás mas "
"insignias."
msgstr ""
"Very well done! You have planted 10 more trees and managed to capture the equivalent "
" CO2 emission of a Motorcycle, Continue taking care of them, soon you will get more "
"badges"

#: .\dashboard\views.py:450
msgid "Avión"
msgstr "Aircraft"

#: .\dashboard\views.py:452
msgid ""
"¡Eres un verdadero héroe del medio ambiente! Has plantado más de 100 árboles "
"y con eso estas contrarrestado en CO2 que produce un avión. Tu dedicación "
"para combatir el cambio climático y proteger nuestro planeta es inspiradora. "
"¡Sigue así!"
msgstr ""
"You are a true environmental hero! You have planted more than 100 trees "
"and with that you are offsetting the CO2 produced by an airplane. Your dedication "
"to fighting climate change and protecting our planet is inspiring."
"Keep it up!"

